        </p>
        <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 14pt; line-height: 120%">
            <i><span style="font-size: 16pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(26,26,26)">In addition to writing nights and weekends, Charles Ives
